Description:
    en: Copy all templates in the project directory lib \ generators to allow customization.
    it: Copia tutti i template nella directory del progetto lib\generators per consentire la personalizzazione.

Example:
    rails generate ergolsca:install

This will create:
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/USAGE
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/ergosca_generator.rb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/_form.html.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/_list.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/edit.html.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/index.html.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/index.js.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/new.html.erb
    lib/generators/erb/ergosca/templates/show.html.erb
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca/USAGE
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca/ergosca_generator.rb
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca/templates/ergosca.css
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca_controller/USAGE
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca_controller/ergosca_controller_generator.rb
    lib/generators/rails/ergosca_controller/templates/controller.rb
